.............<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n把自己鎖在封閉的房間，把窗簾拉上，把頭埋進避世的被窩。或反過來到處周遊列國吃喝玩樂，在陌生的人群中試圖讓自己顯得比較不寂寞。<br />\n<br />\n在朋友的聚會上聽見那個人的消息只好假裝像談論別人的八卦一樣大肆地好奇他的近況，然後把紅酒乾杯後再強顏歡笑地說：&ldquo;其實我早已忘記我們是怎麽分手的啦！&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n或者，瘋狂地結識新對象。用愛情醫療愛情，用付出填補空缺。<br />\n<br />\n不然就不停地為事業奔波，早出晚歸，忙到沒有空檔想起那個人。你用盡任何方式避免自己變成前度的人質。<br />\n<br />\n可惜啊，回憶如果故意要跟你對著幹的話，別傻了，你根本不可能倖免的。"},{"pid":"c2abab9f8970f9282d0f97669f14cf899cf5cff4","tid":592673,"uid":66048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14dccb6f22260789a9ece5384ce86d3faf2b4bb2","tid":592673,"uid":49062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T15:18:18.000Z","msg":"成全...<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T10:06:37.000Z","msg":"佢唱嘅版本真係勁sad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0217809b298563d366f748cbbd619710d10d37b7","tid":592673,"uid":12202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T10:11:34.000Z","msg":"紀念品"},{"pid":"0c4180ea5ffbfb443293ba3bfdd661f148b01dc9","tid":592673,"uid":5709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2abab9f8970f9282d0f97669f14cf899cf5cff4","tid":592673,"uid":66048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14dccb6f22260789a9ece5384ce86d3faf2b4bb2","tid":592673,"uid":49062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T15:18:18.000Z","msg":"成全...<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T10:06:37.000Z","msg":"佢唱嘅版本真係勁sad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T12:12:40.000Z","msg":"Moov 冇呢隻歌聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e